 overblown sound. Following the release of Funeral (2004), which had been recorded in an attic. <a href=\"http://www.last.fm/music/Arcade+Fire/Neon+Bible\">Read more on Last.fm</a>. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply."}}}